      "text": "<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Calibri&quot;,sans-serif\">In a hospital infection control seminar, a discussion arises about the most common types of nosocomial infections. Which of the following is the most common nosocomial infection in hospitals?</span></span></p>",
