      "text": "<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Calibri&quot;,sans-serif\">During an infection control committee meeting, the most common cause of nosocomial infections is being discussed. Which of the following is the commonest cause of nosocomial infection?</span></span></p>",
